description: You are given a mysterious language (codenamed "Secret") available in "Custom Test" tab. Find out what this language is and write a program which outputs its name. Note that the program must be written in this language.
inputFormat: This program has only one test, and it's empty (it doesn't give your program anything to read).
outputFormat: Output the name of the mysterious language.
translation:
本题为愚人节题.
输出要求的一种神秘语言的名称.

By @Fuko_Ibuki
